power at the new Eden.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Confront unique bosses to corner the gun-running market at the megacity and build a future of your own.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360660/extras/f4cabde0aaa5666efa18a8cb0e00c4c2.poster.avif?t=1772589268\" width=780 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360660/extras/f4cabde0aaa5666efa18a8cb0e00c4c2.webm?t=1772589268\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1360660/extras/f4cabde0aaa5666efa18a8cb0e00c4c2.mp4?t=1772589268\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
